executives and how to sell to them.

24
00:01:29.994 --> 00:01:33.920
So let me tell you kind
of how I use this little,

25
00:01:33.920 --> 00:01:40.900
almost like a poem from Rick Rubin, in my
concept around selling a design system.

26
00:01:40.900 --> 00:01:44.640
So, with a design system
what we're trying to do and

