we've got nothing to show.

44
00:02:42.170 --> 00:02:43.704
We have zero value, right?

45
00:02:43.704 --> 00:02:47.251
But I'm sitting down and I'm pitching
to them, that star right above me, and

46
00:02:47.251 --> 00:02:49.909
I'm saying, look,
this is where we're going, right?

47
00:02:49.909 --> 00:02:55.516
This is the idea, the concept, the
aspiration, and what happens is over time,

48
00:02:55.516 --> 00:03:01.136
in reality, we're gonna work now over
time, to build something close to that.

49
00:03:01.136 --> 00:03:03.505
But very quickly, we'll start to plateau.

50
00:03:03.505 --> 00:03:05.181
And as the design system lead,

51
00:03:05.181 --> 00:03:08.607
it's your job to identify what
that next big thing is, right?

52
00:03:08.607 --> 00:03:15.284
You've gotta be thinking ahead,
you have to be, way out thinking ahead.

53
00:03:15.284 --> 00:03:17.789
This is where you're pitching, right?

54
00:03:17.789 --> 00:03:21.495
So we can actually break this
whole thing down right here.

55
00:03:21.495 --> 00:03:25.657
In the next meeting, what I wanna do is
be able to say, this is where we were.

56
00:03:25.657 --> 00:03:29.892
This is the structure of a pitch
that I would make to my leadership.

57
00:03:29.892 --> 00:03:33.334
I would say,
this is where we were last time we met.

58
00:03:33.334 --> 00:03:37.827
And last time we met, I told you,
this is what we would do.

59
00:03:37.827 --> 00:03:42.153
And you invested in me, you invested
in this idea, you were part of this.

60
00:03:42.153 --> 00:03:45.774
And now, this is where we are, right?

61
00:03:45.774 --> 00:03:47.893
We've made great progress.

62
00:03:47.893 --> 00:03:52.972
We've moved our way toward that
aspirational thing that you invested in,

63
00:03:52.972 --> 00:03:55.483
and it took us this much time to do so.

64
00:03:55.483 --> 00:03:58.856
And also, by the way, hey,
we made some really good progress,

65
00:03:58.856 --> 00:04:00.863
don't forget to call this out [LAUGH].

66
00:04:00.863 --> 00:04:04.629
And right on the heels of that,
you have to have ready for

67
00:04:04.629 --> 00:04:07.124
them what the next thing is, right?

68
00:04:07.124 --> 00:04:11.641
This is what we could achieve
together in our next phase of work.

69
00:04:11.641 --> 00:04:16.569
And it's sort of breaking this
concept down into little tiny steps.

70
00:04:16.569 --> 00:04:20.646
So that what you're doing early on is,
maybe it's a little ask, and

71
00:04:20.646 --> 00:04:24.390
