72
00:04:24.390 --> 00:04:27.363
But over time you can start to
take larger risks with that,

73
00:04:27.363 --> 00:04:31.016
and you can earn the trust of those
folks who are investing in this work.

74
00:04:31.016 --> 00:04:32.729
And you can start to see real progress.

75
00:04:32.729 --> 00:04:36.211
They will begin trusting you with this
stuff if you can show a few of this

76
00:04:36.211 --> 00:04:40.124
iterations, where you are actually
meeting the goals you've set with them.

77
00:04:40.124 --> 00:04:41.894
It's a trust building exercise and

78
00:04:41.894 --> 00:04:45.144
it takes time just like everything
else [LAUGH] in design systems.

79
00:04:45.144 --> 00:04:48.238
It's definitely possible to overpromise,
right?

80
00:04:48.238 --> 00:04:53.278
So, I mentioned it's good to start small,
but it's also really good for

81
00:04:53.278 --> 00:04:57.195
you to think about that way,
way out in the future point.

82
00:04:57.195 --> 00:05:00.412
And you're probably gonna be wrong, about
what that is that you're building, right?

83
00:05:00.412 --> 00:05:03.502
But it's good to get those
ideas out of your head,

84
00:05:03.502 --> 00:05:06.753
