87
00:05:12.192 --> 00:05:15.302
And that end point is gonna shift and
change.

88
00:05:15.302 --> 00:05:20.025
And definitely, you've gotta be
careful about over promising here.

89
00:05:20.025 --> 00:05:22.876
And there's lots of other factors
