00:05:27.014 --> 00:05:30.129
But if you're having trouble
shorten the iterations, right?

92
00:05:30.129 --> 00:05:34.486
Try to get a few more conversations with
them, make smaller promises to start and

93
00:05:34.486 --> 00:05:37.193
